      %h2
        = pluralize(@drop.errors.count, "error")
        prohibited this drop from being saved:
      %ul
        - @drop.errors.full_messages.each do |msg|
          %li= msg
  / TODO: Implement separate edit form and use combo boxes
  .field
    = f.label :zone_name
